Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:36.63,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢は風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:44.62,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}梦境如风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}指引着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.27,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}空と雲を…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}将青空和白云…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不吃饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么没有食欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有不爱吃的东西呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃饭的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管吃什么  反正也治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打点滴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样的话  本来能治好的也治不好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的说  应该是「治不好的就是治不好」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为本来就是真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  也要看如何看待这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相当喜欢这个状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很有一种文学性的美感吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种食物玷污自己的身体  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅能品尝一次的  名为「死」的甘美果实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这诱惑总浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关上窗户的话  天使就没办法进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  她会来迎接已经清净身体了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:01.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(注：{\fnふみゴシック\fe128}体を清めた{\r}，为了祭祀等法事而清洁身体)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毫无污瑕的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子又不吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在看着窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是在看那个教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那个不是给人感觉很恐怖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要拆掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  是不是在那里面能看到了什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种话啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会来迎接我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  来的应该是死神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把我带走吧  去那虚无的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁在那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迎接我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  带我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数值有点高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好静养可是不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  饭也好好吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一会儿再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了  天使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我不是什么「天使」了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  你叫作「水银灯」对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在我眼里  你就是一位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来夺走我生命的  黑色天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行和我订下契约的媒介居然是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还快要死掉了  一点力量都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃苹果吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着说刚才的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「爱丽丝游戏」开始之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会用我的生命来和真红战斗对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一样可以轻松解决掉真红
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我也就不需要什么媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气用尽我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这心脏停止跳动吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很遗憾  我不一定能实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次遇到真红  距离现在已是58万小时之前的事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在同一时代苏醒的事并不经常发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我苏醒了  如果还有别人在沉睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏就不会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样…吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  别抱太大希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个无聊的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这个感觉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是586920小时前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里和真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女的第七人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是个爱耍小聪明的妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这力量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵…很强…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  在那个时候变成了废物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经变成过废物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  输给了真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修好蔷薇少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成爱丽丝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时后  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…父亲大人…把我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了我的生命吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一下子就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指变的很热  心脏像在灼烧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒指？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为医生做了多余的事  让我没能死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是已经濒死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用了你那么一点点力量就变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始的时候  大家都说我活不过5岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们就说只能活到7岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说是10岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间里  大家都很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论再怎么延长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「马上就会死」这一点也是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得还是快点死掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我的「这里」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我并不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个坏掉的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是废物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像天使你一样完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是要成为爱丽丝的完美人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我不会再被迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不在了  快消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊了吗？真红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点小伤害就想把我打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭的  我就把你拆成…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是水银灯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的！我是最适合成为爱丽丝的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以父亲大人才让我复活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  已经够了  今天就只打个招呼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  下次再见面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会把你变成废物的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成永远不可能修好的废物碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有句话  一直想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经把你称作「废物」  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到纯把迷失的布偶和我的手臂唤回的时候  我才明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能注意到那呼唤着自己的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会变成废物的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁从一开始就是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是哪位姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都拥有与爱丽丝相配的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:25.00,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幸せと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:32.99,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}嫌な思い出…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幸福和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}悲伤的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续…唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我唱也是没有意义的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我…只是个废物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  「爱丽丝游戏」是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物什么的  是不应该轻易说出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:14.24,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}優しい今が遠ざかる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今温柔地远离而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:20.17,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}静かな夜  続け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惟有寂静的夜在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:28.15,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}瞬の内に込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在一瞬间充满心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:36.31,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}すがる気持ち捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}舍弃依赖的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:44.27,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)}全て思い繋げ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)}将所有思念紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:22:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  她怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情  都如计划一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯？纯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  一大早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你给我泡一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给你自己来一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  打扫一下房间如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  雏莓  置物架你可以随便使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…疯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见
